-- Japan Monitoring Mitsui O.S.K. Tanker Explosion Investigation in Hormuz
-- Kiyotaka Matsuda
-- 2010-07-30T01:52:57Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-30/japan-monitoring-mitsui-o-s-k-tanker-explosion-investigation-in-hormuz.html

          
          
             Japan’s Transport Minister Seiji
Maehara said he was “paying attention” to an investigation
into an explosion onboard a Mitsui O.S.K. Lines Ltd. oil tanker
near the Strait of Hormuz.  
 The government will take any necessary steps following the
conclusion of the probe, he told reporters in Tokyo today.  
